extends ./base-email.pug

block bodyContent
  tr
    td(style="padding:26px 30px 8px;")
      h1(style="margin:0 0 4px 0;font-size:26px;line-height:1.2;color:#{colors.text.primary};letter-spacing:0.02em;") Activá tu cuenta
      if greetingName
        p(style="margin:0 0 8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#{colors.outline.light};")
          | Hola 
          strong #{greetingName}
          | ,
      else
        p(style="margin:0 0 8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#{colors.outline.light};") Hola,
      p(style="margin:0 0 8px 0;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;color:#{colors.outline.light};")
        | Te dimos acceso a A.kit
        if institutionName
          |  para 
          strong #{institutionName}
        | .
      p(style="margin:0 0 12px 0;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;color:#{colors.outline.light};") Para definir tu contraseña inicial y entrar al panel, usá este enlace:

  tr
    td(style="padding:6px 30px 26px;")
      table(role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border:1px solid #{colors.surface.variantLight};background:#{colors.surface.light};border-radius:16px;box-shadow:0 10px 20px rgba(15,107,104,0.08);")
        tr
          td(style="padding:18px;")
            a(href=activationLink style="display:inline-block;padding:12px 18px;background:#{colors.primary.DEFAULT};color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;border-radius:999px;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;box-shadow:0 8px 16px rgba(15,107,104,0.25);") Activar cuenta
            p(style="margin:12px 0 0 0;font-size:12px;color:#{colors.outline.light};") Si el botón no funciona, copiá y pegá este enlace:
            p(style="margin:6px 0 0 0;padding:10px 12px;background:#{colors.background.light};border:1px dashed #{colors.surface.variantLight};border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;font-family:'Courier New',Courier,monospace;color:#{colors.outline.light};word-break:break-all;") #{activationLink}
            p(style="margin:10px 0 0 0;font-size:12px;color:#{colors.outline.light};") Este enlace vence en 72 horas.

